  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 10th level, your control over your threads has reached new heights, allowing for more precise movements.</p><p> The range of your chakra threads is doubled and you can take the help action as a Bonus Action to a creature attached to your threads.</p><p> You can now connect your threads to 2 creatures at once, including as a part of rolling initiative and if you use your White Technique Proficiency feature, you can make all of the creatures you are connected to take the same general action (Dash, Dodge, Attack, Cast a Jutsu, etc).</p><p></p>",
